cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CC, cs.DS

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and the grammaticalization of prepositions in German.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses corpus-based contextual dispersion and entropy measures to predict the degree of grammaticalization.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses computational methods to analyze language data.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with measuring the complexity of language data.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also less likely but possible as the paper uses statistical measures to analyze language data.
